bio.openEndedText:
After an amazing 25-year in corporate America I decided to retire to spend much more time with my amazing wife an two incredible daughters. Turo has been a ton of fun and we love providing top-notch cars for new friends like you.

We love to travel and lived for a decade in Paris, France and Vancouver, Canada and love everything European and Canadian! We'd still be living in Vancouver if I could have convinced my wife to stay lol!

We love visiting our family in PA (Go Steelers!), NC, and FL! We love Utah's amazing snow, mountains and national parks. Our daughters would say they're place to vacation is Los Cabos, MX and any other place where they can go swim with whale sharks!

You count on us for meticulously maintained vehicles, hot knife through butter-like snow tires and cars that are detailed after every use. No odors. We also tint all our vehicle windows to protect against Utah's powerful high-altitude UV rays and also add clear protective film in the front to stop rock chips and ensure our cars are always looking great!

In summer, we'll see you in the national parks and in winter we'll see you on the slopes!
